thread.title: Scott Ashdown
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Scott Ashdown

author: Scott Ashdown
title: Scott Ashdown
text: Prompt response to online enquiry. Friendly and helpfull response to telephone enquiries. Honoured their price match policy on a really competitive price from another supplier (that did not have a local store). The Nektar Parorama P4 midi controller keyboard was delivered within 2 working days from interstate (as promised) and is exactly what I wanted. Keyboard works like a charm. I got a great deal and am extremely satisfied with the service!
